  "texts": [
    "The remaining types, incl.",
    "(i) vaginal as reported by (Tian et al. 2019) and (Liu et al.",
    "2021; ii) vulvar, round ligament, throphoblastoma, and choriocarcinoma as reported by Liu et al. (2021); (iii) tubal as reported by Liu et al.",
    "(2021), Laios et al. (2020), and Vázquez et al.",
    "(2018); and (iv) primary peritoneal as reported in Laios et al. (2020) and Vázquez et al."
